@startuml
actor Reporter
participant "Bug API" as API
participant "Bug Service" as SVC
database DB
queue "Event Bus" as BUS

Reporter -> API: POST /bugs
API -> SVC: CreateBug(command)
SVC -> SVC: validate()
SVC -> DB: begin transaction
SVC -> DB: insert bug
SVC -> DB: commit
SVC -> BUS: publish BugCreated
API --> Reporter: 201 Created (bug_id)
@enduml
